item.title: ~Danger sign past this point help!~
item.dc:creator: @jc22493 Jc22493
item.description:
@jc22493 wrote:

Placing objects, signs in this case, will not limit which areas are wild and which are not. There is either a ‘nonWild()’ method or ‘isInWilderness()’ method located in the client class. Edit those to your liking, then compile.
